    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can just hop in and go. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
