    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast: a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerhouse delivers linear throttle response through eight individual throttle bodies, paired with a 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) for seamless shifts. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring precision during high-lateral-G maneuvers. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including the critical replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators. While the exterior shows minor evidence of spirited road use, the structural and mechanical integrity remains excellent. Features the weight-saving carbon fiber roof and staggered 19-inch forged alloy wheels. A visceral 8,400 RPM experience that is track-ready yet street-refined.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Regularly serviced. Interior and exterior are well-kept. Runs smooth.",
