    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect blend of performance and comfort. The exterior features a deep midnight blue finish that retains a high gloss, showing only minor signs of road use typical for its age. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, complemented by a fully functional suite of modern technology and a pristine panoramic sunroof. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake service. It drives smoothly with responsive handling and no warning lights. A comprehensive service history is available, documenting its life as a smoke-free, garage-kept commuter. This is a reliable, high-quality choice for anyone seeking luxury without the showroom price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
