    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This model has been subjected to a thorough professional assessment to verify its mechanical integrity and operational excellence. The exterior maintains a commanding presence, complemented by a clean, well-appointed cabin designed for comfort and durability. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated buyer who demands reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 36800.0,
