    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. It runs like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway! If you're looking for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s been well-cared for, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come by and take it for a spin!",
